::Shadow Wing::

She stood at the entrance of the ship looking outside.  She saw the 
preds there with the cargo.  She walked out and looked at them.
"Good day to you all.  I'm glad to see that you brought the energon. 
I will see to it that Ramulus gets the crates.  If there is nothing 
else, I will bid you all a good day."
